---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Read the Terapixel Games privacy policy, including data usage, advertising, cookies, and contact details."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-8">
    <header class="space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-light text-zinc-900">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600">Last updated: February 16, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Terapixel Games is committed to protecting your privacy. This page explains what information may be collected when
        you use our website and games, and how that information may be used.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We may receive limited technical information such as browser type, device details, pages visited, and approximate
        region through analytics, hosting, and advertising services.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We do not ask for sensitive personal information to play our browser games. If you contact us directly, we only
        receive the information you include in your message.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Cookies and Advertising</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        This site may use cookies and similar technologies for performance measurement and to support advertising, including
        Google AdSense. Third-party providers may use cookies to serve and measure ads.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings and ad personalization controls from your ad
        providers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Some games or assets may be delivered from third-party platforms. These services may process data under their own
        privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their policies when using linked or embedded content.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        Our website is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children
        under 13.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Policy Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        We may update this policy as products and services evolve. Any updates will be posted on this page with a revised
        effective date.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-zinc-900">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-700">
        For privacy questions, email
        <a href="mailto:support@terapixel.games" class="underline underline-offset-4 text-zinc-900">support@terapixel.games</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
